     <div class="ca-about-body">
      <h2 class="uw-mini-bar">
       About this site
      </h2>
      <p>
       The campus alerts website is the official news outlet of the
       <a href="http://www.wisc.edu">
        University of Wisconsin-Madison
       </a>
       for communications about campus emergencies and other situations that impact campus operations. The site is jointly managed by  UWPD and University Communications.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        In the  event of a disaster, emergency or or other impact to campus operations, this website will contain regularly updated news, instructions and information.
       </strong>
      </p>
      <h3 class="uw-mini-bar">
       Report an emergency
      </h3>
      <p>
       <strong>
        For immediate assistance:
       </strong>
       Call 911
      </p>
      <h3 class="uw-mini-bar">
       Stay informed
      </h3>
      <p>
       <strong>
        Non-emergency:
       </strong>
       For specific questions regarding your personal safety and security, send an email to
       <a href="mailto:uwpolice@mhub.uwpd.wisc.edu">
        uwpolice@mhub.uwpd.wisc.edu
       </a>
       . Or call UWPD non-emergency line, (608) 264-COPS or (608) 264-2677.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        Sign up for WiscAlerts:
       </strong>
       <a href="http://uwpd.wisc.edu/services/wiscalerts/">
        WiscAlerts
       </a>
       is UW–Madison’s emergency notification system.
       <a href="http://go.wisc.edu/wiscalerts">
        Sign up
       </a>
       to get text, email and phone notifications in case of an emergency on campus.
      </p>
      <h3 class="uw-mini-bar">
       Twitter
      </h3>
      <p>
       The following Twitter feed will feature current campus alerts information in the event of a situation that impacts campus operations. This Twitter account is not updated when campus operations are normal.
      </p>
      <a class="twitter-timeline" data-widget-id="674714053231579136" href="https://twitter.com/WiscAlerts">
       Tweets by @WiscAlerts
      </a>
